      • shouldRetry

        protected boolean shouldRetry(@NotNull
                  Exception e,
                  int tryCount)
        Returns whether we should retry the AsyncTask.call() method when given Exception occurred. Defaults to tryCount < getMaxTryCount().
        Parameters:
        e - the Exception that occurred.
        tryCount - the number of tries already executed.
        Returns:
        true if we should retry.
